extendedInfo.description: Guru Gobind Singh Indraprastha University's app is a free android app promoted by Fgrouptech and is Guru Gobind Singh Indraprastha University located in New Delhi , India. This app provide the web view of GGSIPU website on the  android products . This app is designed to provided applicants and student with all information related to location, courses offered, admission, etc.The GGSIPU App has the following features (currently):1. Easy and fast access to GGSIPU portal.2. Detailed information on courses offered and the free structure.3. Direct access to latest updates/results 4. Download latest results/ notices on SD CardThis app is free to use and is compatible with android 2.3+ devices. You can also share it with your friends.List of colleges under university:    Ambedkar Institute of Advanced Communication Technologies and Research    Amity School of Engineering & Technology(ASET)    Ansal Institute of Technology    Army Institute of Management and Technology, Greater Noida    Bhagwan Parshuram Institute of Technology    Bharati Vidyapeeth's College of Engineering    CBP Government Engineering College    Delhi School of Professional Studies and Research (DSPSR)    G. B.
